long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: NeatLeet is a Chrome extension that enhances your LeetCode experience by seamlessly redirecting you to NeetCodeâ€™s solutions. When you open a LeetCode problem, NeatLeet checks if a solution is available on NeetCode.io. If it is, a convenient pop-up appears on the page, giving you the option to view the NeetCode solution. You can easily minimize, decline, or remove the pop-up, offering a user-friendly and customizable experience.
